title: Armaf Club de Nuit Intense Men 105ml EDT
description: Top Notes (The Energetic Opening): A powerful, fresh, and zesty blast of Lemon, bright Pineapple, crisp Bergamot, tart Black Currant, and juicy Apple. (Starts with a sharp, vibrant citrus that quickly smooths out.)Middle Notes (The Smoky Heart): A sophisticated transition to a floral-spicy heart with smoky, masculine Birch, elegant Rose, and clean Jasmine, creating an addictive, leathery nuance.Base Notes (The Lingering Dry Down): A deep, rich, and long-lasting foundation of creamy Vanilla, warm Ambergris, earthy Patchouli, and sensual Musk.

description: Rasasi Fattan Pour Homme Cologne by Rasasi, With above-average longevity, Rasasi Fattan Pour Homme is a woody and earthy fragrance for men. Fattan in Urban English means awesome person suiting the essence contained within the simple pale green liquid.
